# Design system & UI (Spark)

**Product philosophy:** form serves function — see `ios-product-philosophy.mdc` and `docs/DESIGN_PHILOSOPHY.md`. No decorative UI; every control must earn its place in the core flow.

## HIG
- Semantic system colors only; `.tint()` at app root for accent
- **Typography:** system semantic text styles only — see `docs/TYPOGRAPHY.md` (no custom font families)
- Dynamic Type everywhere — no fixed `font(.system(size:))` for body text
- Light + Dark + RTL; adaptive iPhone + iPad layouts
- SF Symbols for icons; custom bitmaps only for brand assets

## Accessibility (mandatory)
- `.accessibilityLabel`, `.accessibilityHint`, `.accessibilityValue` where needed
- Correct `accessibilityTraits`; support XL Dynamic Type on every screen
- VoiceOver order tested on primary flows

## Localization
- `String(localized:)` / `LocalizedStringKey` — never concatenate localized strings
- Minimum: `en` + `zh-Hans`

## SwiftUI polish
- `.sensoryFeedback` for primary actions (iOS 17+)
- **Liquid Glass**: follow `ios-liquid-glass.mdc` — `.glassEffect()` / Materials only; no opacity fills
- Prefer native materials, safe area, and standard toolbar patterns
- Empty and error states with recovery actions (not blank screens)

## Previews
Include at least: default, dark mode, accessibility size (`.environment(\.sizeCategory, .accessibilityExtraExtraLarge)`).
